{"tid":1150073,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"鰂魚涌得利樓街市走失貓貓 “金仔”","createTime":"2019-05-11T14:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T02:55:16.000Z","uid":94774,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"cd15fde93fb206f48cdc967a18a1c3b5a286f4a9","tid":1150073,"uid":94774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打幫幫忙<br />\n如果見到貓貓&rdquo;金仔&rdquo;既<br />\n請電話聯絡68755802或55338876<br />\n我只係代街市檔老闆上來開post<br />\n希望大家可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apwrifC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapwrifC.png&h=d0003fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxFjDfr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxFjDfr.png&h=9d60dbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DDk68N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DDk68N.png&h=6bee51cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhkfV17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhkfV17.png&h=16676daf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQOUr8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQOUr8O.png&h=801edfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/245077365664902/permalink/1184259481746681?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F245077365664902%2Fpermalink%2F1184259481746681%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=5777fb5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/245077365664902/permalink/1184259481746681?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUpdate(11/5 晚): 發現 #鰂魚涌 #得利樓街市 路口嘅耀才證券同埋兩間菜檔都有裝CCTV，有冇街坊同佢哋比較熟絡可以幫幫手 🙏🙇🏼😭<br />\n<br />\nUpdate(11/5 早): 已致電漁護處查詢，並無收穫<br />\n<br />\nUpdate(11/5 早): 老闆同老闆娘好錫隻貓貓，今日行過見到佢哋冇晒心機😔 講起唔見咗隻貓都眼濕濕😭😭😭 老闆平時好辛勞，做到成點鐘先收鋪，好彩有貓貓陪伴😭，好似家人一樣。狂風大雷雨時⛈，老闆寧願一個人通宵留低陪貓貓，可見佢有幾愛錫貓貓「金仔」，依家突然唔見咗，心情極度低落、難過😭😭。如果有人帶走咗「金仔」，請你必須立即歸還！屋企人亦不會追究！因為你無辦法想像失去家人的痛苦和傷心😭😭😭😭<br />\n<br />\n希望「金仔」快d可以返屋企同家人團聚。大家請幫忙廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n尋貓：「金仔」，街市菜檔貓店長。<br />\n地點： #鰂魚涌 #得利樓 街市菜檔<br />\n菜檔老闆一家好傷心 😭😭，冇晒心機，已經搵咗一日都搵唔到。佢哋唔識上網，我幫手po上嚟求救。<br />\n<br />\n「金仔」性格非常好，個個人都同佢玩得一餐，附近街坊都好鍾意佢。<br />\n<br />\n「金仔」尋晚貪玩走咗入隔離雜貨鋪入面玩，人哋收舖困住左佢（唔係第一次）。菜檔老闆尋晚仲聽到「金仔」喺雜貨鋪入面叫，諗住聽朝雜貨鋪開門佢就會返屋企。點知今朝冇返屋企，朝早問雜貨鋪老闆，佢話冇見過「金仔」🧐。希望大家可以幫手搵下，如果有人帶咗返屋企養都麻煩講一聲。今晚一班街坊同老闆一家都搵左好耐，大家都好傷心。"},{"pid":"08d84e80fad643ee713d860c2584de98c6ab000f","tid":1150073,"uid":70121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30356ad07d70232e1fa8710eadd2c3df0dd17521","tid":1150073,"uid":43720,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"應該係比貓義工偷左"},{"pid":"900862130a6e98fae0e9dfcdfbf54f4326394a87","tid":1150073,"uid":94774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30356ad07d70232e1fa8710eadd2c3df0dd17521","tid":1150073,"uid":43720,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"應該係比貓義工偷左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"希望唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對面舖隻可樂仲係到"},{"pid":"463e814c7e4e38f1158a728c5562c1e3e15e5913","tid":1150073,"uid":181858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a32435188cfea47323604760fb70e22273a8e82","tid":1150073,"uid":198958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"異工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdcff8dcfeed7bb9e38a7e4c4809cedba98aeaa","tid":1150073,"uid":66049,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"同附近啲流浪貓講聲幫忙叫佢返屋企"},{"pid":"a085a62fe65233152f26c8335c90f23abdb49ac7","tid":1150073,"uid":250744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl